WE WANT TO MEET YOU!

Do you have a passion for driving results? Are you an optimist who’s looking for an opportunity to grow your career? Are you a curious learner who thrives on tackling new opportunities and tough challenges? Do you love collaborating with your team to solve problems and embrace the strength of others to accomplish goals? Do you inspire your co-workers and earn their trust and respect in all your interactions?

If so, we want to meet you!

 

At rue21 we’re creating an environment that nurtures talent and attracts people who want to thrive. We’re committed to being the workplace where you’ll want to grow your career.

LIVE YOUR BEST (WORK) LIFE

At rue21 we’re committed to providing career opportunities that are exciting, collaborative, fast paced, and flexible. You’ll be surrounded by coworkers who, like you, take pride in driving the success of the business and each other. Together, we work hard, celebrate our wins, and challenge one another to continue to learn and grow.
